All other artifacts that haven't been added to Iteration3 can be found under Iteration2 *including updated ones 

"Use Case Book a Trip: A client is able to search, identify and select a desired 
connection and proceed to book a trip. The system should avoid suggesting 
connections with unconditional layover durations. You must build some policy (feel 
free to build your own)."

For the policy: all results presented to the user avoid the unconditional layover by the following logic
if the train schedules are not on the same day, then there is a layover and we avoid recommending it


